{"tid":2058404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紐卡素成古天奴新球會大熱","createTime":"2020-06-10T06:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T06:58:49.000Z","uid":165817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dc26e08922277d431546aa820311f5a2c07e9edd","tid":2058404,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"據《法國足球》報導，紐卡素已經和巴塞隆拿取得聯繫，洽談巴西中場古天奴的轉會事宜。<br />\n<br />\n古天奴目前被巴塞隆拿外借到拜仁慕尼黑，拜仁慕尼黑無意留斷他，而他亦同樣不在巴塞隆拿的計劃之內。<br />\n<br />\n《法國足球》指，一旦紐卡素被收購，古天奴最有可能的去向就是紐卡素。<br />\n<br />\n英國《郵報》則表示，雖然沙特財團收購紐卡素的計劃目前遇到阻礙，但最終完成收購的可能性仍然很大。<br />\n<br />\n一旦財團完成收購，紐卡素方面就會對古天奴的轉會亮綠燈。"},{"pid":"805e1855862fa3db2e97176368cc5017ec823fe1","tid":2058404,"uid":232736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"啱佢踢啦 等睇佢笑得好燦爛嘅新相"},{"pid":"e425a3fc7cbf45de6bc84def1b01d8b7d457b8ee","tid":2058404,"uid":172627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:46:14.000Z","msg":"新奧雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c119def920c52f6ca99af89935085e239d3e61b","tid":2058404,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e425a3fc7cbf45de6bc84def1b01d8b7d457b8ee","tid":2058404,"uid":172627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:46:14.000Z","msg":"新奧雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:49:59.000Z","msg":"曼聯名叔"},{"pid":"339d029029c02132ca8779c96ab7db2ead908d8f","tid":2058404,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"805e1855862fa3db2e97176368cc5017ec823fe1","tid":2058404,"uid":232736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"啱佢踢啦 等睇佢笑得好燦爛嘅新相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyHi3EX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyHi3EX.jpg&h=a36de6ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d97613fb7bbc280490b0